law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 342, sec. 12, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 119, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 16, 17(8).
